Package: utf8latex
Type: Package
Title: Package for assisting or automating the process of importing, exporting or converting between datasets and LaTeX documents
Version: 1.0.0
Encoding: UTF-8
Authors@R: c(person(given = "José", family = "Gama", role = c("aut","cre"),email = "jgama@abo.fi"), person(given = "Sergueï", family = "Dachian", role = "aut"), person(given = "Göran", family = "Högnäs", role = "ths"))  
Description: utf8latex assists with importing data stored in text files with Unicode characters and to convert text or data with foreign characters or mathematical symbols to LaTeX.  
    It also escapes UTF8 code points (fixing the "warning: found non-ASCII strings" problem), detects languages, encodings and more.  
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 2.7.0)

